=Description=

"The Open High School of Utah is an online charter high school. OHSU offers an incredible personalized curriculum, individualized learning experiences, caring, state-certified teachers, and the flexibility of studying from your home or wherever else you may be. And because the Open High School of Utah is a public high school, there's no cost to Utah residents to attend - it's free!"


